{"id":877,"date":"2024-02-01T15:54:01","date_gmt":"2024-02-01T15:54:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/?p=877"},"modified":"2024-02-01T15:57:39","modified_gmt":"2024-02-01T15:57:39","slug":"aantreden-nieuw-bestuur-stichting-prasoro","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/2024\/02\/01\/aantreden-nieuw-bestuur-stichting-prasoro\/","title":{"rendered":"Aantreden nieuw bestuur Stichting Prasoro"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft wp-image-893 \" src=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/PHOTO-2023-12-06-18-48-54-1-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"411\" height=\"411\" srcset=\"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/PHOTO-2023-12-06-18-48-54-1-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/PHOTO-2023-12-06-18-48-54-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/PHOTO-2023-12-06-18-48-54-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/PHOTO-2023-12-06-18-48-54-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/PHOTO-2023-12-06-18-48-54-1.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 411px) 100vw, 411px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Per 1 oktober 2023 is er een nieuw bestuur aangetreden bij Prasoro.<\/p>\n<p>Het bestuur bestaat uit de volgende personen (v.l.n.r.):<\/p>\n<p>Natalie Goedschalk-Heerenveen: Voorzitter<\/p>\n<p>Marl\u00e8ne\u00a0Gravenberch: Lid<\/p>\n<p>Ruth Sinkeler: Penningmeester<\/p>\n<p>Susan Groenefelt-Leysner: Secretaris<\/p>\n<p>Radjeni Nirmalsingh: Lid<\/p>\n<p>De komende drie jaren richt dit nieuw bestuur zich op het creeeren van een veilig en stabiel thuis voor de kinderen!<\/p>\n<p>Dit zien zij als hun voornaamste taak.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp; Per 1 oktober 2023 is er een nieuw bestuur aangetreden bij Prasoro. Het bestuur bestaat uit de volgende personen (v.l.n.r.): Natalie Goedschalk-Heerenveen: Voorzitter Marl\u00e8ne\u00a0Gravenberch: Lid Ruth Sinkeler: Penningmeester Susan [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-877","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-nieuws"],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/877","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=877"}],"version-history":[{"count":6,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/877\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":904,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/877\/revisions\/904"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=877"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=877"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/stichtingprasoro.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=877"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}